Piccolo examples (based on Piccolo2D 1.3.* releases.)

How to use: clone this project, pull into your favorite IDE, and include Piccolo2D 1.3.*.
dependencies in your IDE project. Most examples have their own main method. You'll
need Groovy and SWT dependencies, or you can comment out some sources to build just
the examples that depend on Swing. (Use Java 1.5+.)